<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>ExpMC20Event_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`ExpMC20`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>specialized<sp/>event<sp/>template<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework,<sp/>designed<sp/>to<sp/>handle<sp/>data<sp/>specific<sp/>to<sp/>experimental<sp/>Monte<sp/>Carlo<sp/>20<sp/>(MC20)<sp/>events.<sp/>It<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>generic<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>extending<sp/>its<sp/>functionalities<sp/>to<sp/>incorporate<sp/>features<sp/>and<sp/>structures<sp/>relevant<sp/>to<sp/>this<sp/>particular<sp/>dataset.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>high-performance<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>event<sp/>object<sp/>tailored<sp/>for<sp/>experimental<sp/>MC20<sp/>analysis.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>ExpMC20Event_class<sp/>The<sp/>ExpMC20<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`ExpMC20`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>its<sp/>implementation<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>It<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>`EventTemplate`,<sp/>thereby<sp/>gaining<sp/>all<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>functionalities<sp/>for<sp/>event<sp/>indexing,<sp/>weighting,<sp/>and<sp/>tree/branch<sp/>management.<sp/>Its<sp/>primary<sp/>role<sp/>is<sp/>to<sp/>encapsulate<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>object,<sp/>which<sp/>likely<sp/>contains<sp/>specific<sp/>data<sp/>members<sp/>and<sp/>methods<sp/>pertinent<sp/>to<sp/>experimental<sp/>MC20<sp/>events.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>ExpMC20Event_cinit_dealloc<sp/>Constructors<sp/>and<sp/>Destructors</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>during<sp/>object<sp/>allocation.<sp/>It<sp/>initializes<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.exp`.<sp/>Crucially,<sp/>it<sp/>then<sp/>upcasts<sp/>`self.exp`<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>`event_template*`<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>it<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ptr`,<sp/>allowing<sp/>`ExpMC20`<sp/>to<sp/>be<sp/>treated<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>generic<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>while<sp/>still<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>specialized<sp/>C++<sp/>object.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>standard<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer.<sp/>This<sp/>method<sp/>is<sp/>intentionally<sp/>left<sp/>empty,<sp/>as<sp/>initialization<sp/>logic<sp/>is<sp/>handled<sp/>by<sp/>`__cinit__`<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>object.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;destructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>upon<sp/>object<sp/>deallocation.<sp/>It<sp/>deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>object<sp/>pointed<sp/>to<sp/>by<sp/>`self.exp`<sp/>(via<sp/>`self.ptr`),<sp/>ensuring<sp/>proper<sp/>memory<sp/>management<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>event<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
