<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`ExpMC20`<sp/>class<sp/>leverages<sp/>Cython&apos;s<sp/>capabilities<sp/>for<sp/>seamless<sp/>C++<sp/>integration:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class<sp/>ExpMC20`:<sp/>Declares<sp/>`ExpMC20`<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>exp_mc20<sp/>*exp`:<sp/>A<sp/>C++<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>object,<sp/>which<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>C++<sp/>representation<sp/>of<sp/>an<sp/>experimental<sp/>MC20<sp/>event.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`self.ptr<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;event_template*&gt;(self.exp)`:<sp/>This<sp/>line<sp/>demonstrates<sp/>C++<sp/>upcasting,<sp/>where<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>derived<sp/>class<sp/>(`exp_mc20`)<sp/>is<sp/>assigned<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>its<sp/>base<sp/>class<sp/>(`event_template`).<sp/>This<sp/>allows<sp/>`ExpMC20`<sp/>to<sp/>fulfill<sp/>the<sp/>`EventTemplate`<sp/>interface<sp/>while<sp/>internally<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>specific<sp/>`exp_mc20`<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
